---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
import CTA from '../components/sections/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Emily">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-petal-cream via-white to-petal-pearl">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Emily's Photo -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-premium">
            <img
              src="https://petal-culture.syd1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/images/emily/emily-petal-culture.jpg"
              alt="Emily, founder of Petal Culture, professional floral designer"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-petal-eucalyptus rounded-full opacity-20 blur-2xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-24 h-24 bg-petal-terracotta rounded-full opacity-15 blur-xl"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Intro Content -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl text-petal-charcoal mb-6">
            Meet Emily
          </h1>
          <p class="font-script text-2xl text-petal-accent mb-6">
            "Flowers aren't just décor—they set the mood, tell a story, and create memories you'll carry forever."
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            The heart and soul behind Petal Culture, bringing 15 years of passion,
            creativity, and personal touch to every celebration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Emily's Story -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl text-petal-charcoal mb-12 text-center">
          My Story
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8 font-body text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            I've been a florist for 15 years, and in that time I've worked with hundreds of couples,
            families, and businesses to create flowers that don't just look beautiful—they feel personal.
            Every wedding, every celebration, every installation has its own story, and I love being
            the one to help bring it to life.
          </p>

          <p>
            Over the years, I've learned that flowers aren't just décor—they set the mood, they tell
            a story, and they create memories you'll carry forever. I take inspiration from my clients,
            the seasons, and the little details that make each celebration unique. No two designs are
            ever the same, and that's exactly what keeps my creativity alive.
          </p>

          <p>
            I'm fortunate to have formed a unique partnership with <a href="https://www.elderberryevents.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-petal-primary hover:text-petal-charcoal transition-colors underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2">Elderberry Wedding and Event Hire</a>,
            working together to support styling and florals for their customers' events. This partnership
            allows both companies to do what they do best and provide memorable experiences—combining
            Elderberry's experience and trusted name with my style and eye for detail.
          </p>

          <p>
            Existing Elderberry customers should experience no difference, as I've been working closely
            with Elderberry until recently and have a loving relationship with the Elderberry team.
            It's been wonderful to continue these trusted relationships while bringing my own creative
            vision to each celebration.
          </p>

          <p>
            My approach is down-to-earth, collaborative, and a little bit playful. I believe that
            choosing your wedding flowers should be fun, not stressful. I'll guide you through the
            process, take care of all the details, and make sure you actually enjoy the journey along
            the way. At the heart of it all, I care about creating something that feels like you—flowers
            that reflect your style, your story, and your celebration perfectly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-petal-cream/30">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl text-petal-charcoal mb-12">
          My Philosophy
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-petal-circle-pink flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-petal-charcoal mb-3">Personal Connection</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-stone-600">
              Every design starts with understanding you. Your story, your style,
              your vision—these are the foundations of truly personal florals.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-petal-circle-olive flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-petal-charcoal mb-3">Seasonal Beauty</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-stone-600">
              I believe in working with nature's rhythm, choosing flowers that are
              fresh, local, and in season for the most beautiful and sustainable designs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-petal-circle-amber flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h1.5a1.5 1.5 0 011.5 1.5V12M9 10c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1m0 0a1 1 0 01-1-1m1 1v1.5m2.5-1.5H9m1.5 0A1.5 1.5 0 0112 12M9 6h6m-6 3h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-petal-charcoal mb-3">Joyful Process</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-stone-600">
              Planning your flowers should be exciting, not stressful. I'm here to guide
              you with patience, creativity, and a good dose of fun along the way.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Behind the Scenes -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl text-petal-charcoal mb-12 text-center">
          When I'm Not Arranging Flowers
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-stone-600">
            <p>
              I love the outdoors, camping and 4WD adventures with my husband and 2 dogs.
              There's something about disconnecting from everyday life and immersing ourselves
              in nature that keeps me grounded and inspired.
            </p>

            <p>
              You'll often find me exploring local farmers markets at dawn, searching for
              the perfect seasonal blooms and building relationships with the growers who
              share my passion for beautiful, sustainable flowers.
            </p>

            <p>
              I'm constantly learning and growing in my craft—whether it's taking workshops
              on new techniques, studying the latest trends in sustainable floristry, or
              simply observing how light plays with petals in my garden at different times of day.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-petal-stone to-petal-pearl rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-stone-400">
                <svg class="w-24 h-24 opacity-30" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 3a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm12 12H4l4-8 3 6 2-4 3 6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-petal-cream/30">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-center text-petal-charcoal mb-12">
          A Little About My Journey
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-petal-forest mb-2">15</p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-stone-600">Years Experience</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-petal-forest mb-2">300+</p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-stone-600">Celebrations</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-petal-forest mb-2">❤️</p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-stone-600">Partnership</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-petal-forest mb-2">∞</p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-stone-600">Creative Passion</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />
</Layout>